OL,3,CThe 91-year-old DIY store worker who
OL,4,Chas raised #175,000 for charity
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist and
OL,7,Fpresenter Zoe Muldoon met Alan who is
OL,8,Fnominated for the regional Pride of
OL,9,FBritain Fundraiser of the Year award
OL,10,F2024.
OL,12,FA 91-year-old DIY store worker who has
OL,13,Fraised more than #175,000 in memory of
OL,14,Fhis son has been nominated for a Pride
OL,15,Fof Britain award.
OL,17,FAlan Wrigley, from Oldham, has worked
OL,18,Fas a greeter at the homeware chain B&Q
OL,19,Ffor the last 20 years and raises money
OL,20,Ffor various charities.
