OL,3,CThe 91-year-old DIY store worker who
OL,4,Chas raised #175,000 for charity
OL,6,FAs well as collecting cash for
OL,7,Fcharity, he has taken part in bungee
OL,8,Fjumps and swam with sharks to help
OL,9,Ffund wheelchairs for four boys and a
OL,10,Flittle girl's Disneyland trip.
OL,12,FThe 91-year-old started fundraising
OL,13,Falmost three decades ago, after his
OL,14,Feldest son died from a heart attack
OL,15,Fand his grandson passed away.
OL,17,F"A little bit later I started
OL,18,Fcollecting and that just kept me
OL,19,Fgoing", Alan said.
