OL,3,CThe 91-year-old DIY store worker who
OL,4,Chas raised #175,000 for charity
OL,6,FIn May 2022, he was invited to the
OL,7,FQueen's Garden Party at Buckingham
OL,8,FPalace to receive a British Empire
OL,9,FMedal for his fundraising efforts.
OL,11,F"The letter came through the door that
OL,12,FI'd been nominated for it", he said.
OL,13,F"I know I'd done a lot of good things,
OL,14,Fbut so have a lot of other people.
OL,16,F"But I like doing it. It's not
OL,17,Fsomething I'm forced into to, I just
OL,18,Fdo it. I think if I ever retire, I
OL,19,Fthink I'd just give in. You need to
OL,20,Fhave something to keep your mind
OL,21,Fgoing."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
