OL,3,CThe 91-year-old DIY store worker who
OL,4,Chas raised #175,000 for charity
OL,6,FAlan is among four finalists nominated
OL,7,Ffor the Pride of Britain Regional
OL,8,FFundraiser of the Year Award 2024 for
OL,9,Fthe North West.
OL,11,FWhen asked what it would mean if he
OL,12,Fwon, Alan said: "It would be a feather
OL,13,Fin my cap. I would like to win it but
OL,14,FI'm not here for that. I'm here
OL,15,Fbecause I enjoy it."
